Shivah::

Shivah leaded Preborn to his quarters "Here you have... Trainer, your 
Quarters"

The quarter was a medium room with good light, a desk, a computer, a 
bed and a internal comm link. 

"This are sub-group boss's quarters"said Shivah "if you like talk 
with other bot with out leave the room  you just have to type the 
number of his or her quarter in comm link,  and the bot that rest 
there will answer... "
